<%- include('partials/header', { title }) %>

<div class="main-container">
  <header class="app-header">
    <div class="title-container">
      <h1 class="cyber-title"><span>L</span><span>i</span><span>n</span><span>k</span><span>P</span><span>a</span><span>s</span><span>t</span><span class="title-sep">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><span>A</span><span>I</span></h1>
    </div>
    <p class="app-description">我的项目列表 · 重命名便于记忆与检索</p>
  </header>

  <div class="content-area">
    <div class="card input-card">
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <h3 class="section-title" style="color: var(--primary); font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; margin: 0;">
          <i class="fas fa-folder-open" style="margin-right: 8px; opacity: 0.85;"></i>全部项目
        </h3>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <button type="button" id="projects-go-home" class="cyber-btn cyber-btn-secondary" style="padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> 返回编辑首页
          </button>
          <button type="button" id="projects-logout" class="cyber-btn cyber-btn-secondary" style="padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> 退出
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
        展示名仅用于列表识别，<strong>不会改变</strong>分享链接 <code>/view/xxx</code>。首页「最近项目」仅显示最近 5 条。
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
        你可以直接在本页对每个项目进行：复制链接、系统分享、开启/关闭密码保护（开启后会自动复制「链接+密码」）。
      </p>
      <div id="projects-page-meta" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;"></div>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 12px;">
        <button type="button" id="projects-page-refresh" class="cyber-btn cyber-btn-secondary" style="padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 0.85rem;">
          <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> 刷新列表
        </button>
      </div>
      <div id="projects-page-list" class="projects-list" aria-live="polite"></div>
      <p id="projects-page-empty" style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; display: none;">暂无项目，请先在首页编辑并生成链接。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="app-footer">
    <p class="footer-text">@2026 LinkPaste AI | 粘贴 AI 灵感，分享无限可能</p>
  </footer>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer', { skipMainJs: true, extraScripts: ['/js/projects-list.js'] }) %>
